 graphs, of  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "f= (2*x^4+5*x^3-5*x^2-20*x-12)/(x^3-2*x
^2-x+2)" "6#/%\"fG*&,,*&\"\"#\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"%F)F)*&\"\"&F)*$F+\"\"$F
